<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1362225" n="1"/> 
<opener><salute><lb/>Vir Consultissime at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Excellentissime,
    <lb/>Fautor Honoratissime <abbr><choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice></abbr></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Celebritas Nominis Tui, mea<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> in <rs type="person">fili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
  <lb/>pietas incitat me, ut per hasce labo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ribus Tuis gravissimis obstrepam.
  <lb/>Qui has affert, est mihi <rs type="person">filius</rs> natu
  <lb/>major. Ille hactenus, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter studium
  <lb/>Juris, Mathesin singulariter excoluit,
  <lb/>et quidem eo cum successu, ut multis
  <lb/>in e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> aliquid pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stitisse videretur.
  <lb/>Cum ita<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> nunc optet admitti ad
  <lb/>majora, ut ita loquar, mysteria,
  <lb/>sciamus<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad illa non per alios, quam
  <lb/>per Celeberrimos <rs type="person">Bernoullios</rs> aditum
  <lb/>patere, eundem, ut felicitatis hujus
  <pb facs="1362226" n="2"/> 
  <lb/>compos reddatur, ad Vos mitto. Ro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>go ita<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Te, Vir Excellentissime, obse<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cro<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>, ut <rs type="person">juvenem</rs> huncce consiliis Tuis
  <lb/>juves, ei<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> viam ad sublimem illam,
  <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice><!-- Todo: kontrollieren ob quae oder qua --> propria Vobis dos est, Mathesin
  <lb/>pandas. Nec ille, nec ego quicquam
  <lb/>in nobis desiderari patiemur, quod
  <lb/>Gratitudo requirit. Uti ab Hu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>manitate Tua precibus <rs type="person">Patris</rs>,
  <lb/><rs type="person">filii</rs> salutem ex debito curantis,
  <lb/>datum iri spero, ita de officiis 
  <pb facs="1362228" n="3"/> 
  <lb/>meis, <rs type="person">filii<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice></rs> obsequio Te cer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tissimum reddo. </p>
        <closer>Vale, Vir Ex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cellentissime, et fave <lb/>Tuo ex asse <lb/><signed><rs type="person"
              >Joh. Georgio Scherzio</rs></signed>, <lb/><abbr>Fac.</abbr>
          <abbr>Jurid.</abbr> Seniori <lb/>et Capituli Thomani Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>posito.<note type="comment"
            resp="SG">Propst des Thomas-Kapitels.</note>
          <lb/><dateline><rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2973783">Arge.</rs>
            <lb/><abbr>d.</abbr>
            <date when="1734-04-27">27. <abbr>April.</abbr>
              <lb/>1734</date>.</dateline>
          <address>
            <pb facs="1362229" n="4"/>
            <addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Monsieur <rs type="person">Bernoulli</rs></addrLine>
            <addrLine>Docteur et Professeur</addrLine>
            <addrLine>en droit tres-celebre <choice><orig><g ref="#pp">pp.</g></orig><reg>etc.</reg></choice></addrLine>
            <addrLine>à</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Basle.</addrLine>
          </address></closer>
</div>
</body>
